by talking about HGVs.

10
00:00:55,880 --> 00:00:58,039
PADDY HONKS

11
00:00:58,040 --> 00:01:00,519
That's...me impression of an HGV.

12
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:02,119
Yes, we are, Pad. Thank you.

13
00:01:02,120 --> 00:01:03,599
Because, as you may have heard,

14
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:06,199
Britain is in the grip of an
HGV crisis.

15
