25
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:47,680
Hey, the big leagues.

26
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:51,119
Look at these. The big leagues.

27
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:52,719
Have you driven one of these before?

28
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:55,839
Never dri... I've driven a 22-tonne
dump truck. Right.

29
00:01:55,840 --> 00:01:58,079
But I've never been behind
the wheel of an HGV.

30
00:01:58,080 --> 00:02:00,279
And me dad was an HGV driver.
Was he?

31
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:03,159
Oh yeah. The romance of it.
Did he let you pull the...?

32
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,559
HE HONKS

33
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:08,279
Oh, all that. I'm all over it.
So... I cannot...

34
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:11,399
I think everyone growing up
wants to drive a lorry.

35
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:14,759
I'm nervous about it.
You're nervous? Yeah.

36
00:02:14,760 --> 00:02:16,719
This is the ideal vehicle
for you.

37
00:02:16,720 --> 00:02:18,799
Your trouble is you've been
getting into little sports cars

38
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:21,359
and everything, you've not...
This is you now.

39
00:02:21,360 --> 00:02:25,079
