Do you know what?
I can't even argue, can I?

42
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:30,959
That's got you on.

43
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:33,359
Mine's called Lynda!

44
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:36,320
Hey, do you know what...what's
missing here? What?

45
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:38,559
The little fella. Yeah.

46
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,079
But... How's he gonna get in?

47
00:02:40,080 --> 00:02:41,960
Exactly! How's he gonna get in?
Exactly!

48
00:02:43,080 --> 00:02:45,119
Oh, here we go.

49
