the engine on, Fred, first.

65
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,520
ENGINE STARTS

66
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:51,039
Hey!

67
00:03:51,040 --> 00:03:52,400
Oh!

68
00:03:53,720 --> 00:03:55,999
