I keep looking.

77
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,520
I don't know where the back is.

78
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:32,119
I've driven everything
on Top Gear,

79
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:37,119
from £1,000 bangers
to £4 million supercars,

80
00:04:37,120 --> 00:04:40,000
and this tops the lot.

81
00:04:41,520 --> 00:04:44,799
I've gotta say, Fred, I've got
the biggest grin on my face.

82
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,360
This is fantastic.

83
00:04:48,160 --> 00:04:50,519
What gear are you in?

84
00:04:50,520 --> 00:04:53,719
I "think" third.

85
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:57,799
Well, if the early signs
were anything to go by...

86
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,599
What gear's that?

87
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:02,799
..we were natural-born truckers.

88
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,599
GEAR CRUNCHES

89
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:07,839
which was just as well,
because it turned out someone else

90
00:05:07,840 --> 00:05:11,280
